a.  Affirmers and owners waive trademark rights for the Work, and declare 
    the Work invalid for trademark use. 
b.  Affirmers and owners waive patent rights for the Work, and declare 
    the Work as prior art and invalid for patent use. 
    engage in protecting the Work from being trademarked with this 
license as declaration of choosing to do so from the start. 
 c. Affirmer offers the Work as-is and makes no representations or 
